text: Jody Beckers (born 10 December 1993) is a Dutch compound archer. She represents the Netherlands at international tournaments. Beckers competed at the 2022 European Archery Championships. In July 2022 she became Dutch national champion. She was selected to represent the Netherlands at the 2022 World Games in Birmingham. Together with Mike Schloesser she won the silver medal in the mixed team compound event. Beckers works in a archery wholesaler. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch archers Category:Sportswomen
